text:
Changes made in winter 2015 to Royal Jordanian Cargo UK service   
Sep 23, 2015 eTN   
Royal Jordanian Cargo in the winter 2015/16 season plans to make changes to its UK operation, which results in a combined operation for Cairo, London Heathrow, and Maastricht. Additionally, the airline plans to operate Amman – Cairo – London Heathrow – Maastricht – Amman routing once a week, using the Airbus A310 Freighter.
